{"tid":1386475,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(又一喜訊）【逃犯條例】逾3千會計師聯署函特首 促政府回應訴求","createTime":"2019-07-30T10:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:08:17.000Z","uid":167451,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6f6d7a882d1e61a4d2ad1ce0b83130da1b8977a8","tid":1386475,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:56:14.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】立法會會計界議員梁繼昌今早與特首辦主任陳國基會面，並請陳主任轉交一份由<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3800多名會計師聯署致函行政長官的信件，促政府回應訴求。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n會計師聯署表示，對香港政府的管治表現表示極度失望和遺憾，並認為是次爭議的根源來自香港社會缺乏一個民主制度，市民無法有效地從政治渠道、諮詢機制表達訴求及將市民的意願反映在政府的施政當中。我們促請政府回應訴求，成立法定獨立調查委員會，調查及檢討香港政府在修訂《逃犯條例》。7 月 21 日元朗西鐵站的襲擊事件，及重啟政治制度改革以落實普選立法會及行政長官，以平息社會的紛爭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:- <a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E9%80%BE3%E5%8D%83%E6%9C%83%E8%A8%88%E5%B8%AB%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E5%87%BD%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96-%E4%BF%83%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-052700670.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E9%2580%25BE3%25E5%258D%2583%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%2587%25BD%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596-%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E6%25B1%2582-052700670.html&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCuQRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=d87b4e96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E9%80%BE3%E5%8D%83%E6%9C%83%E8%A8%88%E5%B8%AB%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E5%87%BD%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96-%E4%BF%83%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82-052700670.html</a>"},{"pid":"602a33c2f99b1787fdcc33790abbced737de3a42","tid":1386475,"uid":167451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T10:57:59.000Z","msg":"會計界也動起來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im